<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CookHub | Help Center</title>
    <!-- Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/da12da5f88.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/styles/responsive.css">
    <script src="../js/loadHTML.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #fffaf0;
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #4a2c0d;
        }

        .help-main {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 80px auto 60px;
            padding: 0 16px;
        }

        /* Intro Section */
        .intro-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf0, #fef5e7);
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .intro-image {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .intro-image i {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #ff7d00;
        }

        .intro-title {
            color: #ff7d00;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 44px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 26px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Section General Styling */
        .section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf0, #fef5e7);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #ff7d00;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-divider {
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #ffb74d;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        /* Card Section */
        .card-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card i {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #ff7d00;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #8c705e;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Articles Section */
        .articles-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .articles-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .article {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .article:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .article h3 {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .article p {
            color: #8c705e;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* FAQ Section */
        .faq-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .faq-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .faq-item {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .faq-item h3 {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .faq-item p {
            color: #8c705e;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-title {
            color: #ff7d00;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .contact-text {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 24px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            color: #4a2c0d;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info span {
            color: #ff7d00;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .help-main {
                padding: 0 12px;
                margin: 70px auto 40px;
            }

            .intro-section,
            .section {
                padding: 20px 0;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .intro-title,
            .section-title,
            .contact-title {
                font-size: 24px;
                line-height: 32px;
            }

            .intro-image i {
                font-size: 50px;
            }

            .intro-text,
            .contact-text,
            .contact-info p {
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 22px;
            }

            .card-grid,
            .articles-grid,
            .faq-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .card h3,
            .article h3,
            .faq-item h3 {
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 22px;
            }

            .card p,
            .article p,
            .faq-item p {
                font-size: 13px;
                line-height: 18px;
            }

            .card i {
                font-size: 26px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Begin: Header -->
    <div class="header"></div>
    <!-- End: Header -->

    <!-- Begin: Help Content -->
    <div class="help-main">
        <!-- Intro Section -->
        <div class="intro-section">
            <div class="intro-image">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="intro-title">Welcome to CookHub Help Center</h1>
            <p class="intro-text">Find answers to your questions, explore guidelines, and get support for using CookHub.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card Section -->
        <div class="section card-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Help Center</h2>
            <div class="section-divider"></div>
            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                    <h3>Getting Started</h3>
                    <p>Share recipes by entering ingredients, steps, and photos in your profile. Use the menu to browse or connect.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <i class="fas fa-camera"></i>
                    <h3>Photo Guidelines</h3>
                    <p>Capture clear, bright food photos with natural light. Upload JPG/PNG files under 5MB.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    <h3>Community Guidelines</h3>
                    <p>Stay respectful, share original recipes, and avoid spam. Report issues to maintain positivity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-cog"></i>
                    <h3>Account Management</h3>
                    <p>Update your profile, change password, or manage notifications in settings. Contact support for account issues.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Articles Section -->
        <div class="section articles-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Popular Help Articles</h2>
            <div class="section-divider"></div>
            <div class="articles-grid">
                <div class="article">
                    <h3>How to Format Your Recipe</h3>
                    <p>List ingredients with amounts, then add step-by-step instructions. Note prep time and servings.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="article">
                    <h3>Engaging with the Community</h3>
                    <p>Comment, follow users, and share recipes to connect with food lovers and grow your network.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="article">
                    <h3>Recipe Copyright Guidelines</h3>
                    <p>Use original recipes or credit sources. Donâ€™t copy without permission to respect creators.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="article">
                    <h3>Troubleshooting Issues</h3>
                    <p>Check file size or connection if uploads fail. Reset password or contact support for login problems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <div class="section faq-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="section-divider"></div>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Can I edit my recipes after posting?</h3>
                    <p>Yes, go to your profile, select the recipe, and click "Edit" to update ingredients or steps.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I report inappropriate content?</h3>
                    <p>Use the "Report" option on the recipe or comment to notify our team for review.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What if I forget my password?</h3>
                    <p>Click "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the steps to reset it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Can I delete my account?</h3>
                    <p>Yes, go to account settings and select "Delete Account" to permanently remove your profile.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Section -->
        <div class="section contact-section">
            <h2 class="contact-title">Need More Help?</h2>
            <div class="section-divider"></div>
            <p class="contact-text">Our support team is here to assist you anytime.</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Email: <span>support@cookhub.com</span></p>
                <p>Phone: <span>+1 (555) 987-6543</span></p>
                <p>Support Hours: <span>Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 6 PM (EST)</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End: Help Content -->

    <!-- Begin: Footer -->
    <div class="footer"></div>
    <!-- End: Footer -->
</body>
</html>